<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <!-- Global site tag (gtag.js) - Google Analytics -->
    <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=UA-135284689-1"></script>
    <script>
      window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
      function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
      gtag('js', new Date());
      gtag('config', 'UA-135284689-1');
    </script>
    <title>泥馬霸氣符咒編輯器</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" name="viewport">
  </head>
  <body class="page-initial">
    <section id="theme-editor" class="theme-editor-section">
      <main>
        <div class="container-fluid">
          <div class="row no-gutters">
            <div class="main row no-gutters justify-content-center align-items-center">
              ${require('./components/svg-container.html')}
            </div>
            ${require('./components/edit-panel.html')}
          </div>          
        </div>
      </main>
      <div class="loading-panel">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center h-100">
          <section class="check-section">
            <div class="panel panel-default">
              <div class="panel-heading">
                <div class="text-center text-light">
                  完成啦！
                </div>
                <button class="btn btn-close"><i class="icon-font icon-cancel"></i></button>
              </div>
              <div class="panel-body">
                <div class="preview">
                  <canvas></canvas>
                  <div class="share-col share-url-col col-12">
                    分享網址:
                    <input type="text" class="url" />
                    <button class="btn btn-copy">
                      <i class="fa fa-files-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> 複製
                    </button>
                  </div>
                  <div class="share-col img-url-col col-12 d-none">
                    imgur:
                    <input type="text" class="url" />
                    <button class="btn btn-copy">
                      <i class="fa fa-files-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> 複製
                    </button>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="panel-footer">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                  <button class="btn btn-cancel">
                    <i class="fa fa-pencil" aria-hidden="true"></i><br/>
                    編輯
                  </button>
                  <button class="btn btn-confirm">
                    <i class="fa fa-cloud-upload" aria-hidden="true"></i><br/>
                    上傳imgur
                  </button>
                  <button class="btn btn-download">
                    <i class="fa fa-download" aria-hidden="true"></i><br/>
                    下載圖片
                  </button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center h-100">
          <section class="loading-section text-center">
            <div>
              <i class="fa fa-spinner fa-spin fa-3x fa-fw"></i>
            </div>
            <p class="loading-info">上傳圖片中 ...</p>          
          </section>
          <section class="notice-section">
            <div class="panel">
              <div class="panel-body">
                <p>
                  本頁功能暫不支援你使用的瀏覽器<br/>
                  請改使用Chrome或是Firefox瀏覽器
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>                
          </section>
          <section class="notice-error-section">
            <div class="panel">
              <div class="panel-body">
                <p class="pb-5">
                  讀取資料中發生錯誤，請重整網頁或稍候再進行一次操作。
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="panel-footer text-center">
                <button class="btn btn-confirm">確認</button>
              </div>
            </div>                
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <div class="js-r-modal"></div>
  </body>
</html>